==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
'''{{ARchar|ШӘ / ШӘвҖҚ / вҖҚШӘвҖҚ / вҖҚШӘ}}''' (tДҒвҖҷ)

# The third letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. Its name is {{ARchar|[[ШӘШ§ШЎ]]}} (tДҒвҖҷ) and it has the sound of English '''[[T]]'''. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ШЁ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[Ш«]]}}.
# The fourth letter of the [[Azeri]] alphabet.
# The eighteenth letter of the [[Hausa]] alphabet.
# The third letter of the [[Kashmiri]] alphabet.
# The fifth letter of the [[Kurdish]] alphabet.
# The fourth letter of the [[Pashto]] alphabet.
# The fourth letter of the [[Persian]] alphabet.
# The fourth letter of the [[Punjabi]] ([[Shahmukhi]]) alphabet.
# The fifth letter of the [[Sindhi]] alphabet.
# The fourth letter of the [[Urdu]] alphabet.
# The fifth letter of the [[Uyghur]] alphabet.

===Pronunciation===
'''With [[sukun]]:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩ’</font> = '''t''' (no vowel follows)


'''With [[fathah]]:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩҺ</font> = '''ta'''<br/>
'''With [[alef]] of prolongation:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩҺШ§</font> = '''tДҒ'''


'''With [[kasra]]:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩҗ</font> = '''ti'''<br/>
'''With [[yaa']] of prolongation:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩҗЩҠ</font> = '''tД«'''


'''With [[damma]]:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩҸ</font> = '''tu'''<br/>
'''With [[waaw]] of prolongation:'''
:*<font size="5">ШӘЩҸЩҲ</font> = '''tЕ«'''

